  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>\"<a href=\"/index.php/Illyrio_Mopatis\" title=\"Illyrio Mopatis\">Illyrio</a> does not play <a href=\"/index.php/Cyvasse\" title=\"Cyvasse\">cyvasse</a>.\" — <a href=\"/index.php/Haldon\" title=\"Haldon\">Haldon</a> <br /><i>No</i>, thought <a href=\"/index.php/Tyrion_Lannister\" title=\"Tyrion Lannister\"> the dwarf</a>, <i>he plays the <b>game of thrones</b>...</i><sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd14.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd14.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p><div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd14.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd14.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_14\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 14\">Chapter 14</a>, Tyrion IV.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260405015708\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.012 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.013 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 96/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8414/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 321/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 22/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 525/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    7.103      1 -total\n100.00%    7.103      1 Template:Ref\n 66.44%    4.719      1 Template:Ref/core\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:29608-0!canonical and timestamp 20260405015708 and revision id 275321\n -->\n",
